For a moment the drones were having a similar problem as anyone else would - they couldn't see and were standing perfectly still as if like statues. The base itself located at the center of this cavern appeared to be largely undamaged, although smoke poured from within it. However the spark of Rodimus does not appear to be coming from the base itself, but instead from Skorponok, who is parked just beside it. Skorponok is just a silent as the rest of things in here.

(TAG: Perceptor)

"Something happened to the programming nodule!" Vorpal transmitted to Darkfate, "It was infected with something. Check on the new minion."

(TAG: Darkfate)
